00:05:08.629 --> 00:05:11.629
We can read about their life, their experiences.

00:05:11.629 --> 00:05:17.629
First as though they're on the sidelines in a sense having completed the race and now they're cheering us on.

00:05:17.629 --> 00:05:18.629
Finish it.

00:05:18.629 --> 00:05:23.629
Look at our problems. Look at the things we've done in spite of difficulties that we've had to face.

00:05:23.629 --> 00:05:27.629
You can do it too. That's basically what they're telling us.

