00:05:44.629 --> 00:05:48.629
And little by little a person can drift away, but we don't want that to happen to us.

00:05:48.629 --> 00:05:52.629
In fact, we can become very anxious about certain things.

00:05:52.629 --> 00:05:57.629
A key phrase that's good to keep in mind is reduce anxiety.

00:05:57.629 --> 00:06:03.629
Whatever we can eliminate from our life to do away with anxiety is of benefit to us.

00:06:03.629 --> 00:06:10.629
