00:06:10.629 --> 00:06:14.629
And we do have some wonderful examples of past runners.

00:06:14.629 --> 00:06:24.629
Hannah, Ruth, Jeopardhys daughter, Abigail, Moses, Joshua, Caleb, and so many more.

00:06:24.629 --> 00:06:27.629
So we want to imitate their faith.

00:06:27.629 --> 00:06:29.629
Isn't that a wonderful publication we have?

00:06:29.629 --> 00:06:31.629
To imitate their faith.

00:06:31.629 --> 00:06:35.629
It's a pleasant thing to take an evening, perhaps each week.

00:06:35.629 --> 00:06:42.629
And with your mate or with your roommate, go over a chapter of it. Read it out loud and cover the material.

00:06:42.629 --> 00:06:44.629
It's very inspiring.

00:06:44.629 --> 00:06:46.629
And we know we can finish the race.

00:06:46.629 --> 00:06:49.629
We're going to do just what Jesus said.

00:06:49.629 --> 00:06:54.629
The one that has endured to the end is the one that will be saved.

00:06:54.629 --> 00:06:58.629
Just stick with it and give Jehovah our best.
